text: It is amusing how narratives change with higher stock prices.... @realmoney @dougkass @seabreezelp
Everyone deserves to make a living but some prudence should be in order, Chuck.

$80 million market cap! Trades $100k worth of stock daily. $1 stock. I dont know a thing about the name and dont care about it but this is sub optimal to even tweet about this gewgaw. Bad optics. Advisors like this all over Twitter - gets traders/investors into trouble...

The new game in town is the business of "advising." Those that don't manage, "advise"... Keep your children and portfolios away from all paid "advisors." Paid "advisors" lack any objectivity. I won't name names but they and you know who they are. Fool me once, shame on you...
